title: Daring Women
resume: Daring Women is a 2010 South Korean television series starring Lee Yoo-ri, Lee Chang-hoon, Seo Ji-young, and Lee Joong-moon. The morning soap opera aired on SBS on Mondays to Fridays at 8:40 a.m. from March 2 to July 30, 2010 for 105 episodes.
